
To build on Debian 9 Stretch, following packages are required :

 * autoconf
 * autoconf-archive
 * automake
 * libtool
 * g++
 * pkg-config

 * libusb-1.0-0-dev
 * libudev-dev
 * libevdev-dev
 * libdbus-1-dev
 * libsm-dev

(Boost libraries)
 * libboost-dev
 * libboost-program-options-dev
 * libboost-system-dev
 * libboost-filesystem-dev
 * libboost-iostreams-dev
 * libboost-serialization-dev

